cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.RO, cs.CV 

The paper proposes a scalable model for learning nonlinear dynamical systems using Gaussian processes. This is a topic that falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), control systems (cs.SY), robotics (cs.RO), and computer vision (cs.CV). The paper specifically focuses on the application of the proposed method to physical flying robotic vehicles, which further supports the relevance of the cs.RO sub-category. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.RO, and cs.CV, in that order.
